Product Description
This DVD is the third installment in the series. This action packed DVD takes viewers on a graphic detailed journey through the highest crime rated neighborhoods in the United States of America. It contains exclusive interviews with real gang members, drug dealers, pimps, and killers. Viewers should be prepared to witness controversial never before seen violent footage. This is reality TV at its best!!!!

This documentary comes filled with disturbing images of how hard life is for the poor in desolate areas of numerous urban centers like Dallas, Cleveland, San Francisco, Boston, and Atlanta, and showcases how many citizens resort to crime in order to get by. This is the only Aquis Bryant video.
